<p>I know this is a necro but <em>holy shit we have readers in Antarctica?!?</em></p>
<p>Also, <em>holy shit, there's internet service in Antarctica?!?</em></p>
<p>Like, how long has this been going on? Do they depend on government satellites to get signals or something, or has some private company agreed to string out wires and erect towers down there? What kind of rates do they get charged? Like, I almost understand why and how Metallica was able to perform down there, but how are they able to get <em>internet?!</em> Also, are we so awesome that people with a bitching job title like <em>Antarctic explorer</em> want to read our stuff on their downtime? That's kickass!!</p>

							</div>

								
					
